  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four people, including a pregnant woman, were the target of wasp stings",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The incident took place today (23) and it is reported that a pregnant woman was also involved.",
        "4 women from Bogavantala \u2013 Bridwell Estate have been targeted for wasp stings.",
        "Meanwhile, the pregnant woman was stung by too many wasps and she was transferred from Pokavantala Hospital to Tikoya Klangan Hospital, according to hospital information."
      ],
